msgid "Supported formats: XMI"
msgstr "Formatos permitidos: XMI"

#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.umbrello.appdata.xml:20
msgid ""
"Several type of diagrams supported: use case, class, sequence, "
"communication, state, activity, component, deployment, entity relationship"
msgstr ""
"Permite usar varios tipos de diagramas: casos de uso, clase, secuencia, "
"comunicación, estado, actividad, componente, despliegue y relación de "
"entidades"

